sql:
SELECT head_of_department 
FROM departments 
WHERE department_id = (SELECT department_id FROM researchers WHERE researcher_id = 0);

external_knowledge:
Patent type names are names of categories of patents; 
Total earnings for each patent is the sum of the amounts in the 'amount' column for each patent; 
This implies that patent earnings are calculated on a per-patent basis.

The patent hierarchy is established based on the patent filing number; 
A patent ID of 0 is assumed to be the root of the hierarchy; 
The level depth refers to the distance from the root patent in the hierarchy.
